A simple example that replaces a data set element with an image element using the BIRT Design Engine API.

A reporting application typically generates a report from a report design. Sometimes business logic requires programmatically changing an existing report design before generating the report.
Here is a simple example that replaces a data set element with an image element using the BIRT Design Engine API to modify the BIRT Design.